       pointer to change.  For example, when the pointer is
       directly over the root window (the backdrop behind all win-
       dows), the pointer has an ``x'' shape.  When you point to
       the inside of a terminal window, the pointer changes to an
       ``I'' shape.  See Figure 1-2.

